If you are signing, please:

* Include your full name in the TITLE of the PR
* Place your name in the list ALPHABETICALLY by FAMILY name
* Please don't include class='highlight' on the LI
* Check your PR after you create it to ensure that you didn't accidentally delete other signatories while editing the file.  While you are editing, other PRs may be merged.

If you want to suggest promoting someone to be a default-visible signatory:

* Name your PR "Highlight {name}"
* Add class='highlight' to their LI
* Explain briefly why they are notable.  This could be that they are a contributor to the text, published author, standards participant, community organiser, or have held national public office
